====Usage note====
Although '''c–Η–Φ–Ω–Α―²–Η―è''' is cognate with '''sympathy''', these words may have different connotations. The Russian '''―¹–Η–Φ–Ω–Α―²–Η―è''' implies attraction, liking or warm feeling, but usually not [[compassion]] or [[condolence]].

